{"tid":1771021,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民主派區議員聯署要求擱置中環「主教山」醫院發展項目","createTime":"2019-12-05T14:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-05T14:25:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62cbc3aad0b4242cf5c3803ad7bf03fdbb983715","tid":1771021,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:07:35.000Z","msg":"民主派區議員聯署要求擱置中環「主教山」發展項目<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496130-20191205.htm?fbclid=IwAR30cWj5QSoqoTlOBbWsCVfJh9yD88DPnR2Dp6k27NnAN_lvy9YZbeAH4Xw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496130-20191205.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR30cWj5QSoqoTlOBbWsCVfJh9yD88DPnR2Dp6k27NnAN_lvy9YZbeAH4Xw&d=9YhXM5wGpBmAIWfwXK7ScLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=3776cfd8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1496130-20191205.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR30cWj5QSoqoTlOBbWsCVfJh9yD88DPnR2Dp6k27NnAN_lvy9YZbeAH4Xw&h=b1cf8b20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1496130-20191205.htm?fbclid=IwAR30cWj5QSoqoTlOBbWsCVfJh9yD88DPnR2Dp6k27NnAN_lvy9YZbeAH4Xw</a><br />\n<br />\n中西區14位現任及候任民主派區議員聯署，要求聖公會及發展局擱置中環「主教山」發展大型醫院項目。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">早前聖公會建議「主教山」建25層高的私家醫院，一直遭民間團體反對。中西區區議員兼立法會議員許智峯表示，項目將破壞主教山歷史價值，影響主教山建築群的景觀及建築風格。他又說，醫院將帶來車流，擔心交通負荷問題。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n政府山關注組的羅雅寧表示，早前規劃會將項目地盤高度限制至主水平基準135米，但該限制與聖公會提出的醫院高度相同，批評政府為聖公會「度身訂造」該醫院項目。<br />\n<br />\n中西區候選區議員任嘉兒表示，自己曾是註冊護士，若興建大型醫院，擔心醫護人手不足及質疑藉次引來外地人才。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯表示，城規會明天會舉行申述會，多個團體表明到場提出反對，不排除會就項目提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">仲諗住點解反對起醫院，原來係</span><span style=\"color: red;\">聖公會</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"58c16dd8018c35d05d96757f7466cabbbb92003c","tid":1771021,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"泛民算唔算百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf31150b6bc6dbd3e34e500b7385b40b478f89ec","tid":1771021,"uid":2076,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y4pN6bO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy4pN6bO.gif&h=f824c62d&s={SIZE}\" />  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見  128 維園見 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MKG48AO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMKG48AO.jpg&h=67817e52&s={SIZE}\" />   <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SrwkGRT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSrwkGRT.jpg&h=06f56243&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba793e8aeb7e18a1295c27b12075527be4a910dc","tid":1771021,"uid":9681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58c16dd8018c35d05d96757f7466cabbbb92003c","tid":1771021,"uid":58841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:12:53.000Z","msg":"泛民算唔算百屌成材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:17:53.000Z","msg":"觀望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c73b426c20e6d000d486c072fdfd352ee9eb47d4","tid":1771021,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-05T14:25:16.000Z","msg":"聖公會真係好腐敗<br />\n小個讀聖公嘅小學已經感覺好差<br />\n啲人由下到上都好功利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}